title: $:/plugins/linonetwo/tw-mobile-sync/develop
creator: LinOnetwo
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

TidGi-Mobile now uses a pre-built HTML from the `tiddlywiki` npm package's `$:/core/save/empty` template (rendered at build time). The old skinny HTML download endpoint and templates have been removed.

This plugin provides Git Smart HTTP endpoints for TidGi-Mobile to sync via `isomorphic-git`.

Use [[SIOC|https://github.com/taurenshaman/semantic-web/blob/cee9e421eed3f31a602f82375fb92fb109d638b7/data/sioc.rdf]] Ontology for server tiddler.
